{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "阿尔贝里亚骑士道 圣都内的逃亡",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "利弗请求赛希尔的协助却遭到拒绝，\\n只好独自寻找从格拉姆斯脱身的机会。\\n期间，他得知赛希尔因救了自己\\n而面临追杀。利弗救下了陷入危机的\\n赛希尔，二人试图摆脱教会骑士。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "要我为了王室而战？\\n不行不行不行！绝对不行！\\n我说不行就是不行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔……你怎么了？\\n我的话怎么让你这么激动？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "正因为你是优秀又高洁的骑士，\\n我才会提出这样的请求……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊、啊啊啊……别和我说话！\\n唔啊啊～别过来！\\n别用你直白的话刺激我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n这种时候，需、需要魔养石！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "咔咔咔……\\n噗哈～哈啊哈啊……\\n总算缓过来了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔……你真的没事吗？\\n你的情绪似乎从刚才开始就不太\\n稳定……还有那块石头是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊……唔……其实……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "原来如此。你不当骑士之后，\\n情绪变得不稳定，\\n所以戒不掉魔养石……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "是的……多亏魔养石我才能保持\\n情绪稳定，但只要一想起骑士道\\n或是忠诚之类的就会变成那样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我总是被骑士时期的遗憾\\n和后悔所压垮。我虽曾担任\\n王的近卫，却没能保护好他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我没有自信，也没有资格\\n再去为他人而战斗了……\\n所以我就辞去了骑士一职。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "因为……\\n我当时……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "当时？\\n辞去骑士一职的时候吗？\\n发生什么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "……\\n没……什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "总之……不管是为了王室而战，\\n还是和你并肩而战，\\n都是不可能的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "那你……\\n为什么要救我呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "因为我想亲自确认被追捕的\\n白燕骑士团团长到底是不是利弗，\\n仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n抱歉，是我强人所难了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "对不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（利弗……还真是一点都没变呢，\\n还像军事学校时期一样。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（再看看我……\\n已经不可能再去\\n帮助别人……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（不过……答应帮他逃离格拉姆斯\\n这点小事应该也没什么吧？\\n可是，我现在这副样子……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊……不行，还是啃魔养石吧……\\n咦，啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "因为刚才的事，\\n已经被啃得这么小了……\\n得买块新的才行……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "什么……干嘛啊你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "白燕骑士团团长在哪！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（赛希尔她……\\n跟以前判若两人。\\n不过也是情有可原。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（她是一位比谁都忠诚的骑士，\\n所以亚罗拉斯王的死\\n才会对她打击那么大吧。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我不能强人所难。\\n还是思考一下怎么\\n独自度过这个难关吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "好了，没问题！\\n可以过去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "商人",
            "context": "真愁人……竟然加强了盘查，\\n弄得人心惶惶的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（盘查更加严格了……\\n看来混在商人里逃出去\\n比较困难吗……嗯？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "怎么了？\\n还没到换班时间呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士3",
            "context": "枢机主教阁下传来了新的命令！\\n说要抓住帮助白燕骑士团团长\\n逃走的女佣兵！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士3",
            "context": "盘查部队这边留下最少的人，\\n其余人立刻前来支援！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "收到！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（可以趁现在守卫薄弱逃出去！\\n不过，他们说的女佣兵\\n该不会是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "都小心她的武器！\\n在各个巷口安排好人手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "别给她利用地形的机会！\\n要让她插翅难逃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（没想到我竟会陷入这种局面……\\n难道当时不救利弗\\n才是最好的选择吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（不……我一定做不到。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（我不可能眼睁睁地看着\\n朋友在自己眼前被追杀……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "好，只要从这堵墙上跳下去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "等她一落地就抓住她！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊啊，真缠人！\\n那就只能朝这边的小路——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "休想跑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "完全被包围了啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "总算追上你了。好了，\\n乖乖交代白燕骑士团\\n团长的下落吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我都说了不知道……\\n你们不是调查过我住的旅馆了么，\\n真是不依不饶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "那只能请你来教会的牢房，\\n慢慢和你聊聊了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啧……啊，诶！？\\n不会吧，没子弹了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "有机可乘！\\n所有人，给我上啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士2",
            "context": "呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士3",
            "context": "唔哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "怎么回事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，抱歉连累你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士1",
            "context": "你是，白燕……呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，快跑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你傻吗！为什么要来救我？\\n趁着他们来追我的间隙\\n跑掉就好了啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你的目的不是\\n回到新阿尔贝里亚吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "嗯……确实如此。\\n但是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我的骑士道不允许我\\n眼睁睁地看着朋友\\n遭到追杀而见死不救。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "是吗……\\n你还真是一点都没变呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士4",
            "context": "他们在那里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "呃，又来追兵了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗，往这边！\\n这里有通往地下水道的台阶！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我们可以从那里出城。\\n虽然容易迷路，但我记得路……\\n我们要利用地形甩掉他们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "嗯，好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_02_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士5",
